## Why combine RAG with a Knowledge Graph?

A vector database answers:

> "What documents are semantically similar?"

A Knowledge Graph answers:

> "How are entities related?"

Example:

User asks:

> Which customers purchased Product A and later opened support tickets related to payment failures?

A vector database may retrieve documents mentioning those topics.

A Knowledge Graph can traverse:

```text
Customer
    │
Purchased
    │
Product A
    │
Opened Ticket
    │
Category
    │
Payment Failure
```

This kind of relationship reasoning is much harder with embeddings alone.

